</span></span></span><![endif]><span style=3D'mso-no-proof:yes'>Rules are i=
n red
and must be satisfied to allow the design to be saved.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=3DMsoListParagraphCxSpLast style=3D'text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l3=
